Class Category

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inlocomedia.android.models.util.JsonableModel
      • com.inlocomedia.android.models.Category
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.inlocomedia.android.models.util.Jsonable, com.inlocomedia.android.resources.api.JSONMapping.Category, java.io.Serializable

    public class Category
extends com.inlocomedia.android.models.util.JsonableModel
implements com.inlocomedia.android.resources.api.JSONMapping.Category
    A Category that contains a id and name. The id is the generic Locale independent key and the name is the translated name of that category on a selected locale.
